title: K.T. Oslin - Live Close By, Visit Often [2001] MAVERICKS
description:
I was really impressed with this offering by K.T. Oslin. It's Country ... but with funky Memphis R&B arrangements ... not as we know it! Live Close By, Visit Often was produced by Raul Malo who also wrote several of the songs. Imagine The Mavericks with a female singer.
